<https://w3id.org/jp-cos/commentary/1000270> schema:hasPart <https://w3id.org/jp-cos/commentary/1000273> .
<https://w3id.org/jp-cos/commentary/1000274> dct:identifier '1000274' ;
  a <https://w3id.org/jp-cos/CommentaryItem> ;
